videos.description: Sean McDonough and Dick Vitale recap Syracuse's 64-62 win over Duke in which Tyler Roberson ties a school record with 12 offensive rebounds.
videos.headline: Vitale praises Roberson's performance

videos.description: Syracuse coach Jim Boeheim breaks down his team's 64-62 win over Duke on the road and praises Tyler Roberson's 14-point, 20-rebound performance.
videos.headline: Boeheim: We played the best defense we've played all year
